title: [SOLVED]820-00165 close lid then open and wont turn on
message:
820-00165 seems to had some prior repair atempt (jtagg removed)

SMC_LID 3.423v when lid is open,
closed lid 0.000v
then open lid, 3.423v

but it wont turn on again, not at key stroke or powerbutton

wil turn on when you plug charger

title: [SOLVED]820-00165 close lid then open and wont turn on
message:
SMC_ONOFF_L 3.425 v when pressing power button no change.

keyboard works for the rest i can use everything except power button

title: [SOLVED]820-00165 close lid then open and wont turn on
message: So bad keyboard and or trackpad/cable for a start. Crap under SMC is likely too, inspect for corrosion.

title: [SOLVED]820-00165 close lid then open and wont turn on
message: SOLVED, crap under SMC, Trackpad cable was also not the best i have seen
